long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,es,et,fa,fi,f: Help check the duplication of URLs in favorite bookmarks and their service status, you can check which URLs are duplicated in favorites, and you can view them according to different statuses of URL services, providing convenient cleaning operations.
long.en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,es_419,uk:
How many URLs in favorites have returned 404 errors? How many are duplicates? How many websites have been shut down? Let's clean them up! 

This Chrome extension helps you check for duplicate URLs in your favorite bookmarks and their service status. You can identify which URLs are duplicated in favorites and view them according to different service statuses, providing a convenient way to clean up your bookmarks.
long.zh_CN: 检测书签里保存的网址重复情况、及其服务状态，提供高效、便捷的清理操作。
long.zh_TW: 檢測書籤裡保存的網址重複情況、及其服務狀態，提供高效、便捷的清理操作。
